Abyssal Monkey is origionally developed by kwevin & others from the isxgames discord
Special thanks for Noobbotter, without his help this update would not have gotten this far.
Current Dev: abandoned
v2.0 Modernization: Claude AI

Start script: Run AbyssalMonkey/AbyssalMonkey
End Script: End AbyssalMonkey

Current Version 2.0.0

=== Version 2.0.0 - Complete Rewrite ===
Architecture:
- Complete OOP rewrite using objectdef pattern
- State machine with obj_StateQueue (17 states for full automation)
- obj_AbyssalConfig for LavishSettings XML persistence
- obj_Logger with configurable levels (CRITICAL/WARNING/INFO/DEBUG)
- Event-driven pulse system using ISXEVE_onFrame attachment

New Features:
- LGUI2 modern UI (AbyssalMonkey.json) with settings panels
- Real-time status display (state, runs, ship HP/cap)
- Drug support with cooldown tracking (Agency Hardshell, Blue Pill, Exile, etc.)
- MTU deployment and retrieval
- Module overheating with heat damage monitoring
- Primary and secondary ammo type support
- Improved drone management with fallback types
- Corp hangar and station container support

Code Quality Improvements:
- Proper ISXEVE.IsReady initialization checks
- (exists) validation on all object/entity access
- Timeout handling for all wait operations
- Error state recovery
- Removed magic numbers (named constants)
- Proper naming conventions

